# Agent YAMLs are REGENERATED by examples/make_fixture.py on every demo run
# (full_loop.sh step 1, the dashboard init, the README quick start). No test
# reads them from disk, so tracking them would only dirty the tree each run.
# The prompt_history*.jsonl artifacts stay TRACKED on purpose: the adversarial
# test consumes the committed data, not the generator.
examples/*_agent.yaml
